{"lemma":"مَلاذَيْ","slug":"مَلاذَيْ","root":"ل.#.ذ","root_slug":"ل-_-ذ","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-_-ذ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n38126","n38913"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B0%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"refuge, shelter"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the root ل و ذ (l w ḏ)."},"ipa":["/ma.laːð/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n38126","headword_ar":"مَلَاذٌ","root":"lw*","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"milowa*apN","text_ar":"مِلْوَذَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter thus in the K and accord. to the TA; but in the TT,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malowa*ap","text_ar":"مَلْوَذَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in the L, without the first vowel-sign;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place to which one has recourse for refuge, protection, preservation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealment; a place of refuge; a refuge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fortress; a fortified place; a castle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n38913","headword_ar":"مَلَّاذٌ","root":"ml*","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who says but does not act,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perform;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a liar;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who behaves in an artificial manner, and is not true in his affection;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maluw*N","text_ar":"مَلُوذٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L [in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"milowa*N","text_ar":"مِلْوَذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and said to be of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minobarN","text_ar":"مِنْبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this seems to be a mistake]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mala*aAnN","text_ar":"مَلَذَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mala*aAniY~N","text_ar":"مَلَذَانِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaA*aniY~N","text_ar":"مَلَاذَنِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [in some copies of the K, by a mistake in the last vowel-sign, each of the last three of these epithets is as though it were syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malo*N","text_ar":"مَلْذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the inf. n of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mala*a","text_ar":"مَلَذَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", “ he lied ” &c.:] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a liar, who, if asked, will not tell truly whence he comes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also all the above epithets: (M, L:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mala*aAnN","text_ar":"مَلَذَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who makes a show of sincerity, faithfulness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honesty, concealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meditating, what is different therefrom."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mal~aA*N","text_ar":"مَلَّاذٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stealthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a wolf. (M, L, K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","L","K"]}]}}